+fn main() {
+    let x = 'a';
+
+    let y = match x {
+        'a'...'b' if false => "one",
+        'a' => "two",
+        'a'...'b' => "three",
+        _ => panic!("what?"),
+    };
+
+    assert_eq!(y, "two");
+}
